gw.bizrules.pcf

Class DefaultBizRulesPageNavigationSupport

  • java.lang.Object
    • gw.bizrules.pcf.DefaultBizRulesPageNavigationSupport
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    BizRulesPageNavigationSupport

    public class DefaultBizRulesPageNavigationSupport
extends java.lang.Object
implements BizRulesPageNavigationSupport
    Default implementation of the business rules navigation support class. Customers can override just the methods they use below in order to accept incremental upgrades to the business rules framework (e.g. side by side comparison).
